{"tid":2456990,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"就是愛子瑜！南韓大地主狂粉蓋「子瑜大樓」獻愛","createTime":"2021-03-22T10:16:30.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-22T12:56:49.000Z","uid":16659,"like":4,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"8c73ad810eda2d5e27df3669a465a0439971f4d5","tid":2456990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:16:30.000Z","msg":"南韓女團twice由9名成員組成，團員有韓國人、日本人還有來自台灣的周子瑜，每個人都有不同的特色，也吸引了各種不同性格的忠實粉絲，在南韓就有一名狂粉因為太喜愛TWICE的關係，竟然在新建房子後以TWICE成員的名字來命名，目前只剩最後一棟「子瑜House」還在興建中，消息曝光後引起網友討論。<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2021/03/22/3076575-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2021%2F03%2F22%2F3076575-PH.jpg&h=2b0a0782&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲TWICE的狂粉興建大樓後以成員名字來命名。（圖／翻攝自TWICE IG）<br />\n<br />\n韓國偶像成功在全世界引起韓流，每到偶像們的生日、出道紀念日等重大日子，各個團體的粉絲總會展開「較勁」，集資贈送各種好東西給自己喜愛的偶像，如「IZ*ONE」成員宮脇咲良本月19日生日時，其粉絲就集資送上高達約4億韓圜（約新台幣1011萬元）的禮物，其中甚至包括一枚1.06克拉的鑽戒，引起討論話題。<br />\n<br />\n而TWICE的粉絲們當然也「輸人不輸陣」，近日就傳出南韓有一名狂粉剛好是大地主，為了證明自己對偶像的愛，他直接興建9棟大樓，並以TWICE成員的名字來幫大樓取名，還將大樓名字高高掛在建物外頭，路過時就可以直接看到「多賢House」、「Sana House」等。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://attach.setn.com/newsimages/2020/05/18/2560043-PH.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fattach.setn.com%2Fnewsimages%2F2020%2F05%2F18%2F2560043-PH.jpg&h=100eb619&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n▲子瑜「專屬」的大樓目前還在興建中。（圖／翻攝自TWICE推特）<br />\n<br />\n據悉，這9棟房子已經有8棟完工，且也已經有人入住，而最後一棟「子瑜House」目前正在大興土木中，消息曝光後同樣引起討論，網友紛紛表示「子瑜是忙內（老么）所以最後蓋嗎？哈哈哈」、「太厲害了吧，這真的是人生目標的那種耶」、「人生勝利組連追星都如此與眾不同」。"},{"pid":"4013e6e57068cdecc0518c8d573e8aaccc22bbf7","tid":2456990,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"我係觀塘都起咗間定延大樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27d667d6f16aee47bb0ca55303899131ae396825","tid":2456990,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:18:01.000Z","msg":"姐係要人入子瑜<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n中門大開"},{"pid":"d6816cceeac802101d6414cae82f18ca4bbcde34","tid":2456990,"uid":242102,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4013e6e57068cdecc0518c8d573e8aaccc22bbf7","tid":2456990,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"我係觀塘都起咗間定延大樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:21:24.000Z","msg":"你想講好多男人都入過去，係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d50adfe80933bb61c1d9497dd6846b8bddab81f0","tid":2456990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4013e6e57068cdecc0518c8d573e8aaccc22bbf7","tid":2456990,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"我係觀塘都起咗間定延大樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:21:34.000Z","msg":"冰有錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c1358855829852326e6aa1f1dab7f950f3bc173","tid":2456990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d6816cceeac802101d6414cae82f18ca4bbcde34","tid":2456990,"uid":242102,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"4013e6e57068cdecc0518c8d573e8aaccc22bbf7","tid":2456990,"uid":33359,"like":5,"dislike":4,"score":1,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:17:16.000Z","msg":"我係觀塘都起咗間定延大樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:21:24.000Z","msg":"你想講好多男人都入過去，係咪？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:22:10.000Z","msg":"米癲拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27e64e80f0259615516e1c360b59972b4eed75c1","tid":2456990,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"27d667d6f16aee47bb0ca55303899131ae396825","tid":2456990,"uid":261849,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T10:18:01.